Taggify,is,a,widget,that,allows,visitors,of,a,web,site,to,add,comments,and,notes,to,the,pictures,on,it,Other,visitors,can,then,see,the,notes,when,they,mouse,over,the,pictures,This,API,allows,users,to,replace,the,native,Taggify,authorization,scheme,with,one,of,their,own,This,allows,the,widget,to,be,integrated,with,membership,websites,like,social,networks,where,multiple,users,can,use,the,widget,Using,custom,authorization,allows,memebers,of,the,website,to,authorize,only,once,on,without,additional,authorization,by,Taggify,widget,In,this,case,the,Taggify,widget,completely,delegates,authorization,to,the,website